---
title: Salmon in a Creamy Dijon Chive Sauce with Roasted Potato Wedges & Lemony Zucchini
description: Looking for a meal that’s light, bright, and super satisfying? You’ve come to the right place! This dish is all that and then some. Salmon fillets are pan-seared until crisp, then served alongside roasted potatoes and lemony zucchini. For a dynamic finish, the salmon is drizzled with a creamy pan sauce. Yeah, you’ll definitely want to keep this delicious recipe in your back pocket.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/61670c5727bc454a694fd451-28604574.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/salmon-in-a-creamy-dijon-chive-sauce-61670c5727bc454a694fd451-46611f4a.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/salmon-in-a-creamy-dijon-chive-sauce-61670c5727bc454a694fd451
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 770 kcal
  fat: 55 g
  saturated fat: 17 g
  carbohydrates: 40 g
  sugar: 9 g
  protein: 35 g
  fiber: 8 g
